  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "Abstract tokens provide a standard interface to: * Mint tokens off-chain as messages * Reify tokens on-chain via smart contract * Dereify tokens back into messages Abstract tokens can comply with existing standards like [ERC-20](./eip-20.md), [ERC-721](./eip-721.md), and [ERC-1155](./eip-1155.md). The standard allows wallets and other applications to better handle *potential* tokens before any consensus-dependent events occur on-chain.",
